[[File:LEGOrganGraft.jpg|thumb|right|200px|A female Shaper performing an organ graft.]]
'''Organ grafting''' was a ritual of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] which involved the replacement of removed organs with a new living creature "augmenting" the Yuuzhan Vong biologically. The [[Executor (Yuuzhan Vong rank)|Executor]] [[Nom Anor]] was known to have removed one of his eyes with the sharpened end of a burning stick and then replaced it with a [[plaeryin bol]], a living creature capable of spitting venom. This was considered one of the most extreme rituals ever committed by a Yuuzhan Vong. Yuuzhan Vong [[Commander/Legends|commanders]] also had [[Command cloak|their cloaks]] attached by special growths to their shoulders. For [[Supreme Commander (Yuuzhan Vong rank)|Supreme Commanders]] and [[Warmaster]]s, it was common for armor plating to be grafted onto their bones.

